## Command Examples
### Testing Welcome Messages
``` bash
# Test with yourself
.testwelcome

# Test with a specific user
.testwelcome @JohnDoe

# Test with user ID
.testwelcome 123456789012345678

# Get system information
.welcomeinfo
```
